'''Pamela Girimbabazi Rugabira''', <ref>[https://web.archive.org/web/20200418010646/https://www.sports-reference.com/olympics/athletes/gi/pamela-girimbabazi-rugabira-1.html "Pamela Girimbabazi Rugabira"], Sports Reference</ref> yavutse ku ya 10 Mutarama 1985,  ni umukinnyi [[Rwanda|w'umunyarwandakazi]] ukina umukino wo koga,   mu mikino Olempike ya 2000, 2004 na 2008; yari afite ibendera ry'u [[Rwanda]] <ref>[https://www.lequipe.fr/Jo/JoFicheAthlete16319.html "Pamela Girimbabazi"] , ''L'Equipe''</ref>.

== ubuzima bwo hambere ==
Mu mikino Olempike ya 2000 ntabwo yigeze agira isomo ryo koga cyangwa umutoza usanzwe. <ref>[https://www.thestar.com/News/World/article/458379 "Beijing's unlikeliest Olympians"], ''The Star'', July 11, 2008</ref> yakuwe mu mikino ya Sydney kubera amategeko ya tekiniki atari amenyereye, hanyuma yiyigisha amategeko abajije kuri interineti. Nyuma, yiyigishije kandi mu gitabo kivuga ibijyanye nuko boga kinyamwuga abifashijwemo na mugenzi we ukomoka mu [[Rwanda]] Jackson Niyomugabo . Yitoje muri pisine ya hoteri ifite metero 25 z'uburebure<ref>https://www.the-sports.org/pamela-girimbabazi-rugabira-swimming-spf653947.html</ref>. Muri metero 50  mbere y'imikino ya Beijing yahagendaga amasegonda 35.  Yananiwe kwitwara neza i Beijing, arangiza ku mwanya wa gatatu kuri bane mukiciro vcye na 88 muri rusange, <ref>[http://www.apanews.net/apa.php?article72686 "Rwandaâ€™s Olympic medal hopes diminish as two of its swimmers go out"], Agence de Presse Africaine, August 15, 2008</ref> akoresheje umwanya wa 39:78sec . <ref>[http://www.newtimes.co.rw/index.php?issue=13624&article=8759 "Two down, two to go as swimmers fail in Beijing"], ''The New Times'', August 16, 2008</ref> Girimbabazi yavuzweho kuba "icyamamare gito" n'ishusho y'umukinnyi w'uzuye, umukinnyi uhatanira gukunda umukino, bitari ugushimishwa no gutsinda cyangwa kuba icyamamare gusa". <ref>[https://www.thestar.com/News/World/article/458379 "Beijing's unlikeliest Olympians"], ''The Star'', July 11, 2008</ref><ref>https://www.newtimes.co.rw/sports/former-olympian-girimbabazi-elected-swimming-body-president</ref>

